text.tspan: Prevalence of bipolar disorder in males vs. females, 2016
Share of the male population versus female population suffering from bipolar disorder. This share has been
age-standardized assuming a constant age structure to compare prevalence between countries and through time.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
